post_text: On January 11th, 2020 the girls(2pm) and boys(4pm) varsity basketball teams will travel to play Fayetteville at the Historic Hickory Gym in Knightstown, Indiana. Tickets are $5 and can be bought at HS home games or the HS office after break. Get yours early, tickets may go fast!
